But you get the idea.

00:02:11.200 --> 00:02:12.330
It's a plane.

00:02:12.330 --> 00:02:15.450
And we're sitting
in three dimensions.

00:02:15.450 --> 00:02:19.370
Now, the other--
so there's more.

00:02:19.370 --> 00:02:22.540
We've only got one-- a
