00:03:44.090 --> 00:03:47.520
In other words, I
believe v equal--

00:03:47.520 --> 00:03:51.280
if I took 1 of the first
and 1 of the third,

00:03:51.280 --> 00:03:56.000
and if I subtracted 2
of the second column--

00:03:56.000 --> 00:04:00.380
so Av will give me 1
of the first column, 1

00:04:00.380 --> 00:04:02.710
of the third column,
and subtracting

00:04:02.710 --> 00:04:05.650
2 of the second column
