00:04:23.300 --> 00:04:29.200
10 times that vector would
still give me 0s and still

00:04:29.200 --> 00:04:30.790
be in the null space.

00:04:30.790 --> 00:04:33.070
So I really have--
the null space

00:04:33.070 --> 00:04:34.720
is a whole line of vectors.

00:04:34.720 --> 00:04:37.660
It's that vector and any
multiple of that vector.

00:04:37.660 --> 00:04:42.240
So it's a whole infinite line,
