00:04:42.240 --> 00:04:44.560
subspace, the null space.

00:04:44.560 --> 00:04:47.180
So the null space
in my picture--

00:04:47.180 --> 00:04:48.680
here is the null space.

00:04:48.680 --> 00:04:54.590
Well, it is not very thick is
