00:06:09.740 --> 00:06:12.770
The other space is one
dimensional, a perpendicular

00:06:12.770 --> 00:06:13.350
line.

00:06:13.350 --> 00:06:15.320
I can show with my
hands, but I can't

00:06:15.320 --> 00:06:17.240
draw on this flat blackboard.

00:06:17.240 --> 00:06:20.800
I have the plane
going infinitely far,

00:06:20.800 --> 00:06:24.240
and I have the line
going perpendicular to it

00:06:24.240 --> 00:06:28.290
and meeting, of course,
