00:06:53.570 --> 00:06:56.440
So what's the column
space of that matrix?

00:06:56.440 --> 00:06:58.460
So the column space
of a matrix, we

00:06:58.460 --> 00:07:01.790
take all combinations
of those three columns.

00:07:04.520 --> 00:07:07.880
And that will fill out a space.

00:07:07.880 --> 00:07:13.958
Now, I have-- so I
