00:08:06.120 --> 00:08:10.570
And that third column can't
contribute anything new.

00:08:10.570 --> 00:08:12.260
It's sitting in
the column space.

00:08:12.260 --> 00:08:14.410
It's a combination of those two.

00:08:14.410 --> 00:08:17.030
But the first two
are independent.

00:08:17.030 --> 00:08:19.580
Their combinations
give the whole plane.

00:08:19.580 --> 00:08:23.290
So the column space
is the whole plane.

00:08:23.290 --> 00:08:24.180
Column space.

00:08:29.770 --> 00:08:33.070
There's not much room
for our fourth subspace.

00:08:33.070 --> 00:08:37.110
But the fourth subspace, in
