00:09:12.680 --> 00:09:16.970
So by transposing a matrix,
it turns these two rows

00:09:16.970 --> 00:09:17.845
into two columns.

00:09:20.750 --> 00:09:22.080
And that's what I have here.

00:09:22.080 --> 00:09:25.600
The row space is the--
this is the column

00:09:25.600 --> 00:09:28.890
space of the transpose matrix.

00:09:28.890 --> 00:09:29.510
I like it.

00:09:29.510 --> 00:09:32.840
I don't want to introduce a
